com.complexible.common.rdf.model

Interface Namespaces

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<org.openrdf.model.Namespace>

    public interface Namespaces
extends Iterable<org.openrdf.model.Namespace>
    A simple class used for management of namespaces. It stores mappings from prefixes to URIs represented as Namespace objects. This class, as a minimum, provides iteration over stored namespaces. Some implementations provide modification functions to add or remove namespaces.
    Since:
    1.0.1
    Version:
    3.1
    Author:
    Evren Sirin

      • add

        boolean add(String thePrefix,
            String theNamespace)
     throws NamespacesException
        Adds a new namespace prefix to the namespaces. If there is a previous namespace defined for the prefix, it will be overridden.
        Returns:
        true if the namespaces has been modified as a result of this call or false if the prefix is already mapped to the same namespace
        Throws:
        NamespacesException
